"cv-thumb-list type-step\">\n                    <li>\n                      <p class=\"th-label\">1단계</p>\n                      <p class=\"th-thumb\">\n                        \n                      </p>\n                      <p class=\"th-cont\">‘PASS’ 앱을 실행하세요.</p>\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                      <p class=\"th-label\">2단계</p>\n                      <p class=\"th-thumb\">\n                        \n                      </p>\n                      <p class=\"th-cont\">메인화면에서 ‘PASS투데이’ 관련 배너를 선택하세요.</p>\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                      <p class=\"th-label\">3단계</p>\n                      <p class=\"th-thumb\">\n                        \n                      </p>\n                      <p class=\"th-cont\">유료 운세컨텐츠의 미리보기 팝업에서 [자세히 보기] 버튼을 선택하세요.</p>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n\n                <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n                  <ul class=\"cv-thumb-list type-step\">\n                    <li>\n                      <p class=\"th-label\">4단계</p>\n                      <p class=\"th-thumb\">\n                        \n                      </p>\n                      <p class=\"th-cont\">\n                        ‘PASS투데이’ 유료 서비스 이용약관을 확인한 후 [PASS투데이 유료가입] 을 누르세요.\n                      </p>\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                      <p class=\"th-label\">5단계</p>\n                      <p class=\"th-thumb\">\n                        \n                      </p>\n                      <p class=\"th-cont\">등록한 ‘PASS’ 앱 비밀번호를 입력하세요.</p>\n                    </li>\n                    <li>\n                      <p class=\"th-label\">6단계</p>\n                      <p class=\"th-thumb\">\n                        \n                      </p>\n                      <p class=\"th-cont\">‘PASS투데이’ 유료 서비스를 이용하세요.</p>\n                    </li>\n                  </ul>\n                </div>\n  